Dr. Sheldon Cooper doesn't.

07:32.340 --> 07:36.140
I suppose that's one
way to look at it.

07:36.140 --> 07:38.910
I think it's the only
way to look at it.

07:38.910 --> 07:40.810
Are you going to
help me or not?

07:40.810 --> 07:43.280
Probably. I'm just
enjoying the foreplay.

07:44.450 --> 07:46.850
Does this mean you are done
mocking my acting career?

07:46.850 --> 07:49.950
Oh, I'm sorry, I thought
making the transition

07:49.960 --> 07:51.820
from actor to acting teacher

07:51.820 --> 07:53.190
was the signal
that one's career

07:53.190 --> 07:55.330
had reached the
end of the road.

07:56.760 --> 07:58.180
Forget it.

07:58.180 --> 07:59.660
I'll pay you $40.

07:59.670 --> 08:02.220
Saturday, 9:00 a.m.
Bring cash.

08:04.340 --> 08:06.570
Raj, I have amazing news!

08:06.570 --> 08:07.540
