08:07.540 --> 08:08.890
I just got offered
a fellowship

08:08.890 --> 08:10.880
at the Weitzmann
Institute in Israel.

08:10.880 --> 08:12.640
Dude, that's incredible!
I know.

08:12.640 --> 08:15.550
