<i>An Actor Prepares,</i>

09:25.680 --> 09:27.850
Stella Adler's
<i>The Technique of Acting,</i>

09:27.850 --> 09:29.420
Uta Hagen's
<i>Respect for Acting,</i>

09:29.420 --> 09:32.790
