<i>Ayyy, I'm an Actor.</i>

09:32.790 --> 09:34.690
Well, good for you.

09:34.690 --> 09:36.640
Come on in.

09:36.640 --> 09:37.760
How shall we begin?

09:37.760 --> 09:39.460
