move around in the space.

09:48.040 --> 09:50.820
You know,
just do whatever feels natural.

09:58.280 --> 09:59.450
Sheldon?

09:59.450 --> 10:02.150
You said to do whatever
feels natural.

10:02.150 --> 10:04.090
This feels natural.

10:04.840 --> 10:06.120
Certainly more natural

10:06.120 --> 10:07.920
than what you're doing.

10:07.930 --> 10:09.190
Come on,
you got to work with me.

10:09.190 --> 10:10.930
